---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="保房服务" description="律金盾房产保全专项服务 - 断供预警、法拍前处置，帮您守住房产">
  <Header />

  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark-900 via-dark-800 to-dark-700 text-white py-16 relative">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-400 via-gold-500 to-gold-400"></div>
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">保房服务</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">房产保全专项服务 · 帮您守住房产</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <!-- 主介绍 -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark-800 mb-6">产品四：房产保全专项服务</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
              <p>房地产下行周期，大量房产面临断供、法拍风险。律金盾提供专业的房产保全服务，在合法合规的前提下，帮您守住最核心的家庭资产。</p>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark-800 mt-8 mb-4">服务内容</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                  <span class="text-xl">🛡️</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-dark-800 mb-2">断供预警期介入</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">协商银行延期、重组房贷，防止进入法拍程序</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                  <span class="text-xl">⚡</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-dark-800 mb-2">法拍前紧急处置</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">评估最优处置方案，守住房产价值</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                  <span class="text-xl">🔄</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-dark-800 mb-2">以房抵债与转售策略</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">在不得不处置时，最大化保全家庭利益</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                  <span class="text-xl">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-dark-800 mb-2">共同财产隔离与保护</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">依法规划夫妻/家庭财产结构</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-gold-50 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-dark-800 text-sm font-medium">适用人群：房贷断供风险户、收到银行催收通知、房产已被查封的债务人</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 保险资产保全 -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark-800 mb-6">产品五：保险资产保全服务</h2>
            <div class="bg-dark-800 rounded-lg p-4 inline-block mb-4">
              <span class="text-gold-400 text-sm font-bold">差异化核心竞争力</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">创始⼈30年保险高管背景，这是市场上最高专业壁垒的稀缺服务。</p>

            <h3 class="font-semibold text-dark-800 mb-4">服务内容：</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold-500 mt-1">•</span>解答核心疑问：我的保单能被强制执行吗？现金价值会被冻结吗？</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold-500 mt-1">•</span>保单现金价值保全方案：依法规避被执行风险</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold-500 mt-1">•</span>受益人变更与保单架构优化</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold-500 mt-1">•</span>保单贷款作为应急资金通道规划</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold-500 mt-1">•</span>年金险/增额寿险资产隔离专项规划</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gold-500 mt-1">•</span>家庭成员保单（配偶/子女）安全性评估与保全</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-gold-50 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-dark-800 text-sm font-medium">参考价格：保险资产保全 1,000-5,000元（顾问费制）</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- CTA -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-gold-500 text-dark-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gold-400 transition-colors text-lg">
              立即咨询，守护您的资产
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
